description:
Jared just moved into town a few weeks ago from California. He needed to make some extra money and have a little fun...
Apparently Jared is big into nude beaches and when he lived in California his favorite haunt was Black's Beach in San Diego.
Black's is one of my favorite hangouts too and we had a good time swapping stories. You know, I'm going to have to make a trip to San Diego here pretty soon...
title: Jared
